code: @Override public void flatMap(String value, Collector<Tuple2<String, Integer>> out) {     // normalize and split the line     String[] tokens = value.toLowerCase().split("\\W+").     // emit the pairs     for (String token : tokens) {         if (token.length() > 0) {             out.collect(new Tuple2<String, Integer>(token, 1)).         }     } }
